title: Saturday ratings: ABC's college football coverage beats Fox on Saturday - US TV
text: ABC's college football coverage topped Fox's own game on Saturday (October 10), according to Nielsen figures.Florida State vs Miami reached 1.0 (3.25m) at 8pm on ABC. Â© Getty Images / Peter G. Aiken Meanwhile, Fox's own telecast of TCU vs Kansas State garnered 0.8 (2.69m) at 8pm.ABC won the key 18-49 demographic on Saturday with 1.0.Over on CBS, 48 Hours attracted 0.7 (4.7m) at 10pm.
